---
title: Greek-Inspired Chicken Breasts and Couscous Salad with Lemon Cream
description: Dill-garlic dusted chicken thighs seared to golden-brown perfection are paired with a couscous Greek Salad. This Mediterranean-inspired meal is brightened with a dollop of lemon cream for a punch of flavour!
